OL,3,CViolent incident reports quadruple in
OL,4,CDumfries and Galloway schools since
OL,5,C2019
OL,7,FThe number of violent and aggressive
OL,8,Fincidents reported in schools in
OL,9,FDumfries and Galloway has increased by
OL,10,F450 percent in the last six years.
OL,12,FData released by the local authority
OL,13,Fin response to ITV Border's Freedom of
OL,14,FInformation requests shows there were
OL,15,F88 reports in the academic year 2019/
OL,16,F20.
OL,18,FIn 2023/24 there were 528 reports, and
OL,19,Fin the last academic year there were
OL,20,F485.
