OL,5,C2019
OL,7,FIncidents recorded in the data include
OL,8,Fphysical violence, as well as verbal
OL,9,Fand written abuse.
OL,11,FSarahjane Moffat, the EIS teaching
OL,12,Funion's representative for the region,
OL,13,Fsays teachers are 'burnt out' and
OL,14,Fleaving the profession.
OL,16,FShe said the Scottish Government
OL,17,Fneeded to provide more funding to
OL,18,Fimprove staffing in schools,
OL,19,Fparticularly when it comes to helping
OL,20,Fchildren with additional support needs.
