OL,7,FPhil McGroggan, Dumfries & Galloway's
OL,8,FUnison representative, said he'd heard
OL,9,Fabout other teachers being "bitten and
OL,10,Fscratched", and that some school staff
OL,11,Fhad even resorted to wearing
OL,12,F"protective gloves".
OL,14,FJenny Gilruth MSP, the Education
OL,15,FSecretary, told ITV Border that such
OL,16,Fbehaviour was unacceptable, and said
OL,17,Fthe Scottish Government's budget
OL,18,Fcommitted an extra #29m to help
OL,19,Fschools support those with additional
OL,20,Fsupport needs.
