OL,7,FShe was criticised by the opposition
OL,8,Fparties for not taking action quickly
OL,9,Fenough, and for failing to announce
OL,10,Fspecific new measures in a ministerial
OL,11,Fstatement at Holyrood this afternoon
OL,12,F(9 September).
OL,14,FDumfries and Galloway Council said it
OL,15,Fregularly meets staffing groups and
OL,16,Ftrade unions.
