OL,7,FIn a statement, a spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"Dumfries and Galloway Council take
OL,9,Freports and incidents of violence
OL,10,Fwithin school settings very seriously.
OL,11,FWe have increased ways of reporting
OL,12,Fsuch incidents and are committed to
OL,13,Ftackling the issue."
